않아도 김에 소금간이 되어있고 참기름으로 고소한맛이 있어 간단하게 만들어 먹기 정말 좋고 된장 꽃게탕이랑도 은근 조화가 잘이루어져서 함께 먹으니 맛도 좋았어요 ~   매일 저녁 뭐억을지 고민하게 되는게 오늘뭐먹지 오늘 저녁 레시피로 된장꽃게타이랑 주먹밥 레시피 어떠세요 간단하면서 맛있게 드시기 좋으실꺼 같아요   이글은 CJ로부터 원고료를 지급받아 작성된 글입니다 ​ ​      ","images":["http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141103_13/rmatjdaks00_14149424106574QS0v_JPEG/10.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141103_36/rmatjdaks00_1414942450532wDivQ_JPEG/capture-20141101-115333.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141103_126/rmatjdaks00_1414986156853FgXro_JPEG/capture-20141101-115508.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141103_158/rmatjdaks00_1414986050084wqmzc_JPEG/capture-20141101-120309.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141103_20/rmatjdaks00_14149860495571as5Y_JPEG/capture-20141101-120513.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141103_290/rmatjdaks00_1414986050584GKh8t_JPEG/capture-20141101-120618.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141103_289/rmatjdaks00_1414986051088wSaRP_JPEG/capture-20141101-120645.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141103_78/rmatjdaks00_1414986056389RyW9v_JPEG/capture-20141101-115231.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141103_180/rmatjdaks00_1414986056650UTdJv_JPEG/capture-20141101-115844.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141103_152/rmatjdaks00_1414986057131nL6mE_JPEG/capture-20141101-120008.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141103_161/rmatjdaks00_1414986824206CrK0H_JPEG/capture-20141102-185439.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141103_127/rmatjdaks00_1414986824442oSkTp_JPEG/capture-20141101-121021.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141103_56/rmatjdaks00_1414986824653K6lhh_JPEG/capture-20141101-121341.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141103_43/rmatjdaks00_1414986824894dXVnU_JPEG/capture-20141101-120925.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141103_186/rmatjdaks00_1414986826044AT7AL_JPEG/capture-20141101-121430.jpg?type=","